Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,紧身裙女教师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在想事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我谈谈把
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不用见外嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:02:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,说把
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢讲就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要开始教健康教育
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这样?\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,西田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这么烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能会笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因为学生都用怪异的眼光看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怪异的眼光?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一直很色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很色的看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,(上课中)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,学生这次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,又对我恶作剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,下次要上健康教育
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,下周耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,学生这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你很烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们越来越过分\N过分?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我上次骂了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我为什么叫你来把
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,上课不上课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,都是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这么色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我才无法专心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦
